  "description": {
    "zh": "好吧，我去查了点资料。似乎事情比我一开始想的要复杂得多。显然，这不仅仅只是一些晚上跟踪人的跟踪狂，而是一个完整的邪教团伙，他们在整个地区都留下了他们的痕迹。\n\n我自己没有亲眼看到过那些祭祀场所和标记，所以需要你过去确认一下。你能去检查那些我的团队们称存在祭祀场所的地方吗？\n\n目前不管是不是有上锁的房间都没关系，我只需要你确认那些符号是否存在。",
    "en": "Okay so, I did some digging on this. Seems like there is way more about this than I thought at first. Apparently they are not just some weird people who stalk people at night, there is a whole cult and they leave their traces in the entire region. I did not see the ritual sites and markings myself so I need confirmation from you, can you check the spots out that my guys are claiming that theres those sites?\n\nDoesn't matter for now if there are locked rooms, I just need you to confirm that the symbols are there."
  },
